---
description: Date and time formatting rules (Luxon + date precision)
alwaysApply: true
---

# Dates & Times

Store `event_date` (ISO `yyyy-MM-dd`), optional `event_time` (24h `HH:mm`), and
a `date_precision`: `exact | month | semester | year | approximate | unknown`.

Always render via `formatEventDate(date, time, precision)` in
`src/shared/date.ts` - never format dates ad hoc. It uses Luxon presets:

- exact -> `DATE_SHORT` (`5/14/2011`)
- month -> `May 2011`  |  semester -> `Spring 2011` / `Fall 2011`
- year -> `2011`  |  approximate -> `Around 5/14/2011`  |  unknown -> `Unknown`

Never imply precision the data does not have (e.g. do not show a day for a
`year`-precision date).
